PrecisEnactment of the CES GRANT REGULATIONS which set out the rules for determining eligibility for grants, the conditions to be met before a grant can be paid, the circumstances where a grant must be repaid, and the terms and conditions to be included in an Agreement between the Minister and the trustees of a Registered Education Savings Plan.
